This paper deals with the optimization of network power consumption, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also presents an algorithm that uses ant colony optimization, which is a technique commonly used in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the need for decentralized computation, which is a topic related to distributed computing (cs.DC). Finally, the paper deals with the optimization of energy consumption, which is a topic related to systems (cs.SY) and information theory (cs.IT).
